{"id":231165329,"title":"政府在能源政策上 扮演什麼角色？","content":"http://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg\n\n1. 一如往常的，擁核與擁煤是取決於對風險的認知 ( 認為核電廠會出現核安問題導致核能支持度下滑；意識燃煤造成暖化現象則導致其支持度下滑 )。\n\n2. 研究中也出現雖認知某能源風險，但依舊選擇該能源的參與者。\n\n3. 擁核派多為教育程度高的白人男性，而擁煤者為低教育程度的非裔及拉丁裔女性。\n\n4. 沒有任何族群對能源有單一偏好。相反地，一種能源往往有不同族群支持，且政府在增加民眾能源知識上扮演著重要角色。\n\n所以說，我們台灣政府呢？","excerpt":"1. 一如往常的，擁核與擁煤是取決於對風險的認知 （ 認為核電廠會出現核安問題導致核能支持度下滑；意識燃煤造成暖化現象則導致其支持度下滑 ）。2. 研究中也出現雖認知某能源風險，但依舊選擇該能源的參與者。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["能源","環境","台灣"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"新加坡國立大學","department":"化學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"057d21a3-c420-49cb-8bb2-54c5a4fc1481","url":"https://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z"},{"id":"057d21a3-c420-49cb-8bb2-54c5a4fc1481","url":"http://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","normalizedUrl":"http://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/981FBWe.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-25T14:37:32.604Z"}],"postAvatar":""}